evidence.source_document: Order Granting Plaintiffs' Application for Temporary Restraining Order
evidence.text: The Order Granting Plaintiffs' Application for Temporary Restraining Order (Document 64) grants a TRO to stop federalization of the National Guard but contains no reference to a court-appointed monitor or monitor's report. The document discusses the Governor's Office of Emergency Services monitoring protests (p. 19), but this is not a court-ordered monitor report.

The Docket (tokens 0-10000) contains no filings related to monitor appointments or monitor reports. All entries document case progression through motions, hearings, and filings up to the TRO grant on June 12, 2025.
